what_is_the_rationale_for_your_choice: 1999 films are fairly dated (with it currently being 2015) so I find it more plausible that a film from 1999 is bad than that ALL english language films from any year ever are bad. Plus 1999 is a more narrow category than all English language films, it's more likely the film from one year will be bad than all films of one language ever.
